## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="1c056-315">以下示例将信息写入有关<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar>对象传递给[控制台](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=159613)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1c056-315">The following example writes information about a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> object to the [console](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=159613).</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
  
private static void DumpGrammarStatus(Grammar item)  
{  
  Console.WriteLine("Grammar name is {0}:", item.Name);  
  Console.WriteLine("  The Grammar {0} loaded.",  
    item.Loaded ? "is" : "is not");  
  Console.WriteLine("  The Grammar {0} enabled.",  
    item.Enabled ? "is" : "is not");  
  if (item.RuleName != null)  
  {  
    Console.WriteLine("  The root rule is {0}.", item.RuleName);  
  }  
  else  
  {  
    Console.WriteLine("  The Grammar does not specify a root rule.");  
  }  
}  
```

  
  
